About Milady Meme Coin (LADYS)

LADYS is a decentralized cryptocurrency, started in 2023 by an anonymous team inspired by the popular Milady NFT collection and its community. 
The Milady Maker NFT collection that inspired LADYS token was launched in 2021, and consists of 10,000 generative profile pictures. LADYS is a social token that does not have direct utility within the NFT ecosystem. It is also referred to as memecoin, like PEPE, SHIB, and APE. 
Social tokens are cryptocurrencies that foster engagement and loyalty through membership, access, or rewards within a specific community. 
Pronounced “Lay-dees,” LADYS is an ERC-20 token that is compatible with Ethereum. You can use LADYS to trade and stake digital currencies, as well as participate in the network.
LADYS launched on May 7, 2023.
Today, the most popular uses for LADYS are entertainment and trading. Inspired by the Milady NFT collection, LADYS crypto holders are typically community-led, memecoin traders.
